# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺投資或者賭波輸緊錢嘅時候，盡快賣晒啲嘢或者收手，唔好再蝕多啲。通常用喺股票、外匯、波彩等等嘅情況。 (量詞：吓)
eng:to cut losses
<eg>
yue:今鋪輸到咁犀利，不如早啲止蝕算啦，唔好再焗住落去。 (gam1 pou1 sou1 dou3 gam2 sai1 lei6, bat1 jyu4 zou2 di1 zi2 sik1 syun3 laa1, m4 hou2 zoi3 bak1 zyu6 lok6 heoi3.)
eng:You've lost so badly this time, better cut your losses and stop now, don't force yourself to keep going.
 [end of text]


